ChallengeResponseAuthentication no
ListenAddress <%= @sftp_server_address %>
DenyUsers root daemon bin sys sync games man lp mail news uucp proxy www-data backup list irc gnats nobody libuuid syslog messagebus sshd puppet ntp snmp colord ftp postfix ganglia kernoops pulse rtkit statd munge avahi hplip saned usbmux micuser landscape nagios
AllowUsers <% @accounts.each do |account| %><%= (account == 'id') ? '' : account %> <% end %>
Subsystem sftp internal-sftp
UsePAM yes
X11Forwarding no
AllowTCPForwarding no
ChrootDirectory <%= @sftp_server_data_dir %>/%u
ForceCommand internal-sftp
